ScenarioHeader.Title: Val-ADLS exist query with AO

Query.Query_Text: SELECT B.`S_SUPPKEY`,B.`S_NAME`,B.`S_ADDRESS`,B.`S_NATIONKEY`,B.`S_PHONE`,B.`S_ACCTBAL`,B.`S_COMMENT`,B.`Totalkeys` FROM (SELECT `S_SUPPKEY`,`S_NAME`,`S_ADDRESS`,`S_NATIONKEY`,`S_PHONE`,`S_ACCTBAL`,`S_COMMENT`, `S_SUPPKEY` +  `S_NATIONKEY` AS `Totalkeys` FROM `adls.root`.`TPCH1/Supplier.csv` WHERE `S_NATIONKEY` > 17 ) B
